<p begin="5005000t" end="34617917t" region="bottom" xml:id="subtitle0"><span style="span">[Carole] </span><span style="italic">These platforms</span><br/><span style="italic">which were created to connect us</span></p>
<p begin="35452084t" end="60477084t" region="bottom" xml:id="subtitle1"><span style="italic">have now been weaponized.</span></p>
<p begin="72989584t" end="96346250t" region="top" xml:id="subtitle2"><span style="span">[Brittany] These companies are</span><br/><span style="span">the most powerful in the world</span></p>
<p begin="97180417t" end="131381250t" region="bottom" xml:id="subtitle3"><span style="span">because they own the personal data</span><br/><span style="span">of people from all around the world.</span></p>
<p begin="150567084t" end="186436250t" region="top" xml:id="subtitle4"><span style="span">[Carole] </span><span style="italic">The real game changer</span><br/><span style="italic">was Cambridge Analytica.</span></p>
<p begin="195195000t" end="225225000t" region="bottom" xml:id="subtitle5"><span style="span">[Brittany] </span><span style="italic">We targeted those whose minds</span><br/><span style="italic">we thought we could change.</span></p>
<p begin="246913334t" end="271521250t" region="bottom" xml:id="subtitle6"><span style="span">[David] </span><span style="italic">When people see</span><br/><span style="italic">the extent of the surveillance,</span></p>
<p begin="272355417t" end="293209584t" region="bottom" xml:id="subtitle7"><span style="italic">I think they're going to be shocked.</span></p>
